Title: Unleashed
Plot: Langston and Sara turn to Lady Heather for help in tracking down the culprit responsible for injuring a woman before she was seemingly mauled to death by a mountain lion. Meanwhile, Nick and Dr. Robbins manage to rescue the unborn baby of a teenage girl who appears to have committed suicide
GuestStars: Melinda Clarke, Tony Curran, Abby Brammell, Aaron Hill, Cody Longo, Dylan Neal, Allison Smith, Archie Kao, Marc Vann
